thread.title: BRIEF-Delek Logistics Partners Q4 Revenue $151.2 Million

title: BRIEF-Delek Logistics Partners Q4 Revenue $151.2 Million
text:
Feb 26 (Reuters) - Delek Logistics Partners Lp:
* DELEK LOGISTICS PARTNERS, LP REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 RESULTS
* Q4 REVENUE $151.2 MILLION * QTRLY NET INCOME ATTRIBUTABLE TO ALL PARTNERS OF $0.57 PER DILUTED COMMON LIMITED PARTNER UNIT​
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.64 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* DELEK LOGISTICS - AGREEMENT TO ACQUIRE BIG SPRING LOGISTICS ASSETS WITH ABOUT $40 MILLION OF FORECASTED ANNUAL EBITDA FROM DELEK US​
* SAYS ‍ON FEB 26, 2018, DEFINITIVE AGREEMENT WAS ENTERED INTO WITH DELEK US TO ACQUIRE BIG SPRING LOGISTICS ASSETS​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
